Subject: [PATCH] avcodec/magicyuv: correct end of array check in multi VLC
 parsing

Fixes: out of array write
Fixes: 63390/clusterfuzz-testcase-minimized-ffmpeg_AV_CODEC_ID_MAGICYUV_fuzzer-5144552979431424.fuzz

